\f0\b\fs48 \cf0 Retro:  Back to Basics\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf0 Week 3 - I believe in God but want to be tolerant\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 Intro\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Started a series on the basics of what it means to be a Christian:\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Review of series so far\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Week 1 \'96 Money tends to be our God\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Week 2 \'96 Religion tends to be our distraction\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 Transition:  This week we\'92re going to look at another passage from 1 Corinthians that has to do with how we interact with each other and the world.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 WE\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We struggle with interacting with each other right?\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Divorce rate is the same if not higher\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Churches fight with each other left and right about the dumbest things\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Christians have become known in our country as what we are against than what we are for\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Hypocrisy seems rampant \'96 we talked about this last night\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}(Can use a few more here)\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}At one point in time we had a huge influence over the culture and now we are losing it quickly every day it seems.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 Transition:  Today we\'92re going to talk about why I think all that is and it\'92s because we\'92ve forgotten one of these foundational truths.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 God\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We\'92re going to pick up in the middle of a part of Paul talking to the Corinthians about some person in their church is sinning and what we will see is they are happy about how tolerant they are of each other!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 1 Cor 5\'a0\
3\'a0For I, on my part, though\'a0absent in body but present in spirit, have already judged him who has so committed this, as though I were present.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We live in a culture that continually tells us we can\'92t judge them.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You haven\'92t walked in my shoes\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You don\'92t know my story\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You have lived life with me\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Paul says it doesn\'92t matter\'85I can judge you and have already done so!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He goes so far to say I\'92m not even in the same area and I can judge you.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He doesn\'92t have to know the whole story\'85he just needs to know the parts he already does\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We live in a culture that wants to excuse our own sins and crucify those who sin against us.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s backwards in the Christian faith.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We are called to repent of our sins and take them serious and then forgive others who sin against us.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We have no tolerance for the intolerant!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 4\'a0In the name of our Lord Jesus, when you are assembled, and\'a0I with you in spirit,\'a0with the power of our Lord Jesus,\'a05\'a0I have decided\'a0to\'a0deliver such a one to Satan for the destruction of his flesh, so that his spirit may be saved in\'a0the day of the Lord Jesus.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Some people will say that tolerance loves and intolerance hates.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There are some agendas in today\'92s culture that if you disagree with them then you hate them.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Nothing could be further from the truth!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The goal at the end of this verse is to bring them back and save his soul.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If this world is all there is then judging someone and potentially hurting their feels is terrible rude and insensitive and ridiculous.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But if there is something more then it is the most loving thing a person could do.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf4 Illustration of someone about to get hit by a truck\'85what do you say do?  Or a parent who refuses to tell their child not play in the road because the kid wants to play there.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 6\'a0Your boasting is not good.\'a0Do you not know that\'a0a little leaven leavens the whole lump\'a0of dough?\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Paul says when you allow a little sin in the church and tell everyone it\'92s not a big deal it spreads in the church and compromise starts to take over in a big way.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3  7\'a0Clean out the old leaven so that you may be a new lump, just as you are\'a0in fact\'a0unleavened. For Christ our\'a0Passover also has been sacrificed.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Paul then reminds his people\'85Jesus had to die a brutal death for all that stuff you don\'92t think is a big deal. \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f2\i \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}(explain the Gospel here clearly and slowly)\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f1\i0 \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The reason we celebrate that is because we are now no longer under condemnation of sin or our we slaves to it.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We celebrate the fact that we are a slave to Him now and no longer a slave to our lusts\'85don\'92t you see the disconnect?\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 8\'a0Therefore let us celebrate the feast,\'a0not with old leaven, nor with the leaven of malice and wickedness, but with the unleavened bread of sincerity and truth.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Here\'92s what he is asking them\'85do you really believe what you celebrate when you take communion?  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Think about that for a second.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When we take communion today in a few moments\'85do you really believe what we celebrate?\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 Transition:  he goes on to explain what all this means\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf3 9\'a0I wrote you in my letter\'a0not to associate with immoral people;\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So this is a conversation they are having back and forth and Paul has already told them how to handle people and situations like this\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 10\'a0I\'a0did\'a0not at all\'a0mean\'a0with the immoral people of this world, or with the covetous and swindlers, or with\'a0idolaters, for then you would have to go out of the world.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He says\'85listen\'85don\'92t avoid people who are not Christians who act contrary to what we believe\'85if you did that you\'92ve have to leave the world.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There are people who do this\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They believe the world is the problem and if they can get rid of the world then they will be ok\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They don\'92t realize or want to admit that we are the problem\'85our hearts are the problem\'85the world just reveals them.  \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 11\'a0But actually, I wrote to you not to associate\'a0with any so-called brother if he is an immoral person, or covetous, or\'a0an idolater, or a reviler, or a drunkard, or a swindler\'97not even to eat with such a one.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Paul says you\'92ve got it all backwards\'85you\'92re not associating with the wrong people.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If someone says they are a Christian but is acting in a way that is contrary to what we believe and is not repentant about it\'85don\'92t associate with them.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If someone is not a Christian but acting really any way\'85have lunch with them, get to know them, pray for them, love them, tell them about Jesus.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For too long the church has been known for what we are against\'85not because we are against our own but because we are against everyone else.  We\'92ve looked our own people and said it ok but looked at the world and said they are all wrong!  It\'92s backwards\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 12\'a0For what have I to do with judging\'a0outsiders?\'a0Do you not judge those who are within\'a0the church?\'a013\'a0But those who are outside, God\'a0judges.\'a0Remove the wicked man.  1 Cor 5\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls13\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Our job as Christians is not judge the world but to judge each other.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We\'92ve gotten it backwards for years and that is the problem with our country and our world today.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We have no right\'85you have no right to tell someone who is not a Christian they are wrong.  NONE!  That is God\'92s job to convict them.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We are called to tell them about Jesus and the hope that comes with Him but no right to use the Bible to make someone who doesn\'92t agree with that standard to feel bad.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 Transition:  Now there is always that person who doesn\'92t know anything about the Bible but one verse they have memorize for other people when they feel judged and it\'92s this\'85\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf3 7\'a0\'93Do not judge so that you will not be judged.\'a0\
\
2\'a0For in the way you judge, you will be judged; and by your standard of measure, it will be measured to you.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls14\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We\'92re going to come back to this one is a second\'85we\'92ve really messed up this first part\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We\'92ll skip down a few verses\'85to verse 5\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 5\'a0You hypocrite, first take the log out of your own eye, and then you will see clearly to take the speck out of your brother\'92s eye.  Matthew 7\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls15\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The issue is hypocrisy\'85judging isn\'92t\'92 wrong\'85hypocrisy is wrong!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But I want to go back to the first two verses as we wrap up today and say one last thing\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 2\'a0For in the way you judge, you will be judged; and by your standard of measure, it will be measured to you.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls16\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is powerful and comes with a promise and here is what I think has happened in our country\'85and I\'92m not trying to be political or take a stand on something\'85I\'92m explaining what I\'92m seeing.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For years we had all the power and influence and we used it.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls16\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We didn\'92t judge each other much like the Corinthian church\'85but tried to control others who aren\'92t Christians with our power in the government.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And they cried foul and said \'93But we don\'92t believe this\'85why should we have to follow and obey something we don\'92t believe?\'94  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Essentially we told people it was good for them and so \
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls16\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You don\'92t have a choice in whether you can keep the baby or not\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You don\'92t have a choice in who you want to marry or not\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls16\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But it\'92s morally wrong is what some will say but that isn\'92t your grid with which to make a law and you know it!\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls16\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Lying is morally wrong\'85who wants to create a law where you go to jail if you lie.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Dishonoring your parents is a sin!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Anyone want to make those illegal?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There was a political leader who had 2 divorces and cheated on both previous wives but stood up preached about family values and the sanctity of marriage!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls16\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Now we\'92ve lost influence haven\'92t we?\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls16\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And culture has shifted away from us and I hear almost daily from conservative Christians about how they are being persecuted and forced to do things and behave in ways they don\'92t agree with!\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls16\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Why should I have to legally be a part of a ceremony I don\'92t agree with\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Why should my tax dollars go toward something I don\'92t support like abortion\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls16\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Why am I being forced to behave in a way that I don\'92t agree with or think is right.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And now culture looks at us with the same disgust we had for other groups of people and tells us it is good for culture to be loving and accepting and open about new ideas\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92m not trying to say any of this is right \'96 on either side\'85I\'92m pointing out what happens and there is a part of that sits back and watches what is happening and I think to myself\'85we sort of deserve this.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s our fault!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls16\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}See we judged culture when we weren\'92t supposed to!\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls16\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jesus says it comes back around if you do it wrong so be careful.\
